The paper focuses on the impact of RF impairments on mm-wave communication using OFDM waveforms, which falls under the domain of information theory (cs.IT) and communication (cs.COMM). The study also involves evaluating the link performance and channel estimation, which can be categorized under systems and control (cs.SY). The use of mm-wave communication and OFDM modulation also relates to multimedia (cs.MM) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
